"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?28/21/29013?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Depression treatment options for adolescents (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?21/24/21894?source=see_link\">",
